I used to have this doll! Can't remember what she was called. It took me a little bit of searching, but I finally made out the tag: J Cey doll

I remember thinking she was the coolest thing, with that real bar of soap, sponge, bottle, change of clothes... and human-sized Kleenex! (LOL, I never did understand that one!)
